room_title: Escape room "Abstract Larceny" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
room_description: Your squad of trainee security guards has let a gang of notorious art thieves abscond with your museum’s most valuable exhibits! You could report it to the curators, but you’d rather not get fired (again), and rent is due soon… Instead, you’ve made your way to gang’s lair. Recover the goods and make it back to the museum before anyone knows what happened!
